---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Accordion from '../components/Accordion.astro';
import ScrollReveal from '../components/ScrollReveal.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Lancashire County Council | Reform UK in Control | Tom Pickup"
  description="What Reform UK is delivering at Lancashire County Council. Budget discipline, protected services, and transparency across all departments."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="lcc-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <ScrollReveal>
        <div class="lcc-hero-inner">
          <span class="badge badge-teal">Reform UK &middot; 53 of 84 Seats</span>
          <h1>Lancashire County Council</h1>
          <p class="lcc-hero-sub">
            Reform won a historic landslide in May 2025. Here&rsquo;s what we&rsquo;re delivering
            for 1.2 million Lancashire residents.
          </p>
        </div>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Achievements -->
  <section class="lcc-achievements">
    <div class="container">
      <ScrollReveal>
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-heading">What We&rsquo;ve Done</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">Reform&rsquo;s first year running Lancashire County Council</p>
        </div>

        <div class="achievement-grid stagger-children">
          <div class="achievement-card">
            <div class="achievement-icon" style="--card-accent: #12b6cf">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="23 6 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 1 18"></polyline><polyline points="17 6 23 6 23 12"></polyline></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>3.80% Council Tax Rise</h3>
            <p>The lowest in 12 years. After 7 years of maximum rises under the Conservatives, we delivered restraint without cutting front-line services.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="achievement-card">
            <div class="achievement-icon" style="--card-accent: #ff9f0a">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2v20M17 5H9.5a3.5 3.5 0 0 0 0 7h5a3.5 3.5 0 0 1 0 7H6"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>&pound;28M Overspend: Nearly Eliminated</h3>
            <p>Inherited a &pound;28 million projected overspend. Cut it to &pound;6.1 million and falling through targeted action, not blanket cuts.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="achievement-card">
            <div class="achievement-icon" style="--card-accent: #30d158">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 0 0 0-7.78z"></path></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>5 Care Homes: Saved</h3>
            <p>The Conservatives began consultation on closing five county care homes. We listened to 1,600+ residents and secured their future with new investment.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="achievement-card">
            <div class="achievement-icon" style="--card-accent: #bf5af2">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>&pound;350M Bond Losses: Exposed</h3>
            <p>&pound;519 million invested in VeLTIP bonds now worth an estimated &pound;169 million. The Conservatives failed to transparently report the true scale of these paper losses.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="achievement-card">
            <div class="achievement-icon" style="--card-accent: #ff453a">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="1" y="4" width="22" height="16" rx="2" ry="2"></rect><line x1="1" y1="10" x2="23" y2="10"></line></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>Pension Directorships: Ended</h3>
            <p>Stopped councillors collecting additional salaries for sitting on the Lancashire Pension Fund board. Public service, not personal gain.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="achievement-card">
            <div class="achievement-icon" style="--card-accent: #ffd60a">
              <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"></path><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline><line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line><line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line></svg>
            </div>
            <h3>&pound;1.33 Billion Balanced Budget</h3>
            <p>Delivered a balanced budget for 2025-26 with a &pound;62 million savings programme and improved savings delivery rates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Departments & Services -->
  <section class="lcc-departments">
    <div class="container">
      <ScrollReveal>
        <div class="section-header">
          <h2 class="section-heading">Services &amp; Departments</h2>
          <p class="section-subtitle">What the county council is responsible for &mdash; and what we&rsquo;re doing about it</p>
        </div>

        <div class="departments-list stagger-children">
          <Accordion title="Education & Schools" defaultOpen={true}>
            <div class="dept-content">
              <p class="dept-summary">Lancashire County Council is responsible for school admissions, SEND provision, school transport, and education support services across the county.</p>
              <div class="dept-stats">
                <div class="dept-stat">
                  <span class="dept-stat-value">600+</span>
                  <span class="dept-stat-label">Schools in Lancashire</span>
                </div>
                <div class="dept-stat">
                  <span class="dept-stat-value">180,000+</span>
                  <span class="dept-stat-label">School-Age Children</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="dept-detail">SEND provision remains one of the most challenging areas. The county faces a significant deficit in the Dedicated Schools Grant high needs block, reflecting a national crisis in special educational needs funding that predates Reform taking control.</p>
            </div>
          </Accordion>

          <Accordion title="Children's Social Care">
            <div class="dept-content">
              <p class="dept-summary">Safeguarding children, looked-after children services, fostering and adoption, early help and family support.</p>
              <div class="dept-stats">
                <div class="dept-stat">
                  <span class="dept-stat-value">&pound;250M+</span>
                  <span class="dept-stat-label">Annual Budget</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="dept-detail">Children&rsquo;s social care is the single largest pressure on county council finances nationally. We&rsquo;re working to improve early intervention while managing caseload demand.</p>
            </div>
          </Accordion>

          <Accordion title="Adult Social Care">
            <div class="dept-content">
              <p class="dept-summary">Care for elderly and disabled adults, care home provision, domiciliary care, mental health support, and safeguarding.</p>
              <div class="dept-stats">
                <div class="dept-stat">
                  <span class="dept-stat-value">5</span>
                  <span class="dept-stat-label">County Care Homes Saved</span>
                </div>
                <div class="dept-stat">
                  <span class="dept-stat-value">1,600+</span>
                  <span class="dept-stat-label">Residents Consulted</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="dept-detail">We reversed the previous administration&rsquo;s plans to close five county-run care homes after listening to residents and families. New investment has been pledged to secure their long-term future.</p>
            </div>
          </Accordion>

          <Accordion title="Highways & Transport">
            <div class="dept-content">
              <p class="dept-summary">Road maintenance, potholes, street lighting, traffic management, public transport coordination, and school transport.</p>
              <div class="dept-stats">
                <div class="dept-stat">
                  <span class="dept-stat-value">7,400 km</span>
                  <span class="dept-stat-label">Road Network</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="dept-detail">Lancashire&rsquo;s road network is one of the largest in the country. Years of underinvestment left a significant maintenance backlog. We&rsquo;re prioritising the most dangerous defects while pushing for fairer national funding.</p>
            </div>
          </Accordion>

          <Accordion title="Public Health">
            <div class="dept-content">
              <p class="dept-summary">Health improvement, disease prevention, health protection, and reducing health inequalities across Lancashire.</p>
              <p class="dept-detail">Public health responsibilities transferred to county councils in 2013. The service covers smoking cessation, substance misuse, sexual health, obesity programmes, and health visiting.</p>
            </div>
          </Accordion>

          <Accordion title="Waste & Environment">
            <div class="dept-content">
              <p class="dept-summary">Waste disposal (not collection &mdash; that&rsquo;s district), household waste recycling centres, minerals and waste planning.</p>
              <p class="dept-detail">The county council is the waste disposal authority, responsible for processing and disposing of waste collected by the 12 district councils. This includes managing household waste recycling centres and the county&rsquo;s long-term waste strategy.</p>
            </div>
          </Accordion>

          <Accordion title="Libraries & Culture">
            <div class="dept-content">
              <p class="dept-summary">Public library service, museums, archives, and cultural services across Lancashire.</p>
              <div class="dept-stats">
                <div class="dept-stat">
                  <span class="dept-stat-value">64</span>
                  <span class="dept-stat-label">Libraries Across Lancashire</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="dept-detail">Libraries serve as vital community hubs, particularly in deprived areas. We&rsquo;re committed to maintaining this essential service while exploring innovative ways to increase footfall and value.</p>
            </div>
          </Accordion>

          <Accordion title="Trading Standards">
            <div class="dept-content">
              <p class="dept-summary">Consumer protection, fair trading, product safety, underage sales enforcement, and scam prevention.</p>
              <p class="dept-detail">Trading Standards protects both consumers and legitimate businesses. The service investigates rogue traders, doorstep crime, and counterfeit goods while supporting compliant businesses.</p>
            </div>
          </Accordion>

          <Accordion title="Fire & Rescue Service">
            <div class="dept-content">
              <p class="dept-summary">Part of the county council structure. Provides fire prevention, emergency response, and community safety across Lancashire.</p>
              <div class="dept-stats">
                <div class="dept-stat">
                  <span class="dept-stat-value">39</span>
                  <span class="dept-stat-label">Fire Stations</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="dept-detail">Lancashire Fire and Rescue Service operates under the governance of the county council&rsquo;s Combined Fire Authority. It covers fire response, road traffic collision rescue, flood response, and community fire safety.</p>
            </div>
          </Accordion>

          <Accordion title="Corporate Services & Finance">
            <div class="dept-content">
              <p class="dept-summary">Council finances, HR, IT, legal services, property management, procurement, and democratic services.</p>
              <div class="dept-stats">
                <div class="dept-stat">
                  <span class="dept-stat-value">&pound;1.33B</span>
                  <span class="dept-stat-label">Total Budget 2025-26</span>
                </div>
                <div class="dept-stat">
                  <span class="dept-stat-value">&pound;62M</span>
                  <span class="dept-stat-label">Savings Programme</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <p class="dept-detail">We&rsquo;re driving efficiency across corporate services, ending wasteful spending habits, and improving savings delivery from the 48% rate inherited from the Conservatives.</p>
            </div>
          </Accordion>
        </div>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact CTA -->
  <section class="lcc-contact">
    <div class="container">
      <ScrollReveal>
        <div class="contact-cta-card">
          <div class="contact-cta-lines"></div>
          <div class="contact-cta-inner">
            <h2>Questions About the County Council?</h2>
            <p>Whether it&rsquo;s about highways, schools, social care, or council finances &mdash; I&rsquo;m here to help.</p>
            <a href="/contact/" class="cta-btn-white">Get in Touch</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </ScrollReveal>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* ---- Hero ---- */
  .lcc-hero {
    padding: var(--space-2xl) 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .lcc-hero-inner {
    max-width: 680px;
  }

  .lcc-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    line-height: 1.08;
    margin: var(--space-md) 0 var(--space-md);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 0%, var(--accent) 100%);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    background-clip: text;
  }

  .lcc-hero-sub {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    max-width: 560px;
  }

  /* ---- Achievements ---- */
  .lcc-achievements {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .achievement-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .achievement-card {
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background: rgba(28, 28, 30, 0.5);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    transition: border-color var(--transition-normal), transform var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .achievement-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }

  .achievement-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--card-accent) 15%, transparent);
    color: var(--card-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .achievement-card h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .achievement-card p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  /* ---- Departments ---- */
  .lcc-departments {
    padding: 0 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .departments-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .dept-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .dept-summary {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.65;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .dept-detail {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .dept-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .dept-stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
    padding: var(--space-md);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    min-width: 140px;
  }

  .dept-stat-value {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .dept-stat-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  /* ---- Contact CTA ---- */
  .lcc-contact {
    padding: 0 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .contact-cta-card {
    position: relative;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 20% 80%, rgba(18, 182, 207, 0.4) 0%, transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(135deg, #0a2a3a 0%, #12b6cf 100%);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--space-xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .contact-cta-lines {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(
        135deg,
        transparent,
        transparent 40px,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 40px,
        rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03) 41px
      );
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .contact-cta-inner {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: 500px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .contact-cta-inner h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #ffffff;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .contact-cta-inner p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .cta-btn-white {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.7rem 1.75rem;
    background: #ffffff;
    color: #0a2a3a;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    text-decoration: none;
    background-image: none;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    transition: transform var(--transition-fast), box-shadow var(--transition-normal);
  }

  .cta-btn-white:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    background-image: none;
    background-size: 0;
  }

  /* ---- Responsive ---- */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .achievement-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .lcc-hero {
      padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-lg);
    }

    .dept-stats {
      flex-direction: column;
    }

    .dept-stat {
      min-width: unset;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .achievement-card {
      padding: var(--space-md);
    }
  }
</style>
